                  </persName>
             sworn. - Examined by Mr. Abbott. I am nephew to the last witness: On the 20th of April I received from her two ten-pound Bank-notes, which I took to David Jones.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18000917-46-person474">
                  DAVID 
                  JONES
